I think this app is the best of it's kind by a huge margin. The only thing I would change, or rather add, is the ability to record the X/Y editing in the app.  I've spoken with the developer about adding this feature a while ago.  But it sounded like he thought it might make the app more complex than most users would want or can handle, not quoting him on this though.  But I would absolutely love the ability to record myself, screwing around with the X/Y effects pad.  Even if it meant this had to be implemented into a second application, well, I would be first in line to purchase, said app. 5 stars all the way. GTab 10.1 / ICS 4.0.1
